		{ ref: `1 Corinthians 15:58`, slug: `1-corinthians`, ch: 15, text: `Therefore, be steadfast, immovable, always abounding in the work of your Father, knowing that in Him your labor is not in vain.`, note: `Not one spreadsheet, setup, or late night is wasted — your labor is never in vain in Him.` },
